{"title_page": "Vincent Blore", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2015}}\n{{Use British English|date=May 2015}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = Vincent Blore\n| image               = \n| fullname            = \n| height              =  \n| birth_date          = {{Birth date |1907|2|25|df=y}}\n| birth_place         = [[Uttoxeter]], England\n| death_date          = {{death year and age|1997|1907}}\n| position            = [[Goalkeeper (association football)|Goalkeeper]]\n| years1              =\n| clubs1              = Uttoxeter Amateurs\n| years2              = {{0|000}}?\u20131932\n| clubs2              = [[Burton Town F.C.|Burton Town]]\n| years3              = 1932\u20131933\n| clubs3              = [[Aston Villa F.C.|Aston Villa]]\n| caps3               = 0\n| goals3              = 0\n| years4              = 1933\u201335\n| clubs4              = [[Derby County F.C.|Derby County]]\n| caps4               = 15\n| goals4              = 0\n| years5              = 1935\u201336\n| clubs5              = [[West Ham United F.C.|West Ham United]]\n| caps5               = 9\n| goals5              = 0\n| years6              = 1936\u201338\n| clubs6              = [[Crystal Palace F.C.|Crystal Palace]]\n| caps6               = 33\n| goals6              = 0\n| years7              = 1938\u2013{{0|000}}?\n| clubs7              = [[Exeter City F.C.|Exeter City]]\n| caps7               = \n| goals7              =\n\n}}\n'''Vincent P. Blore''' (25 February 1907 \u2013 1997)<ref name=\"whustats\">{{cite web | url=http://www.westhamstats.info/westham.php?west=2&ham=62&united=Vincent_Blore| title=Welcome to the Wonderful World of West Ham United Statistics&nbsp;\u2014 Vincent Blore | publisher=www.westhamstats.info | accessdate=11 December 2014}}</ref> also known as '''Vince Blore''' was an English [[association football|footballer]] who played as a [[goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for Uttoxeter Amateurs, [[Burton Town F.C.|Burton Town]], [[Aston Villa F.C.|Aston Villa]], [[Derby County F.C.|Derby County]], [[West Ham United F.C.|West Ham United]], [[Crystal Palace F.C.|Crystal Palace]] and [[Exeter City F.C.|Exeter City]].\n\n==Footballing career==\nBlore played for Uttoxeter Amateurs, [[Burton Town F.C.|Burton Town]] and Aston Villa before moving to Derby County in August 1933.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.astonvillaplayerdatabase.com/134.html | title=Blore, Vincent P. \"Vic\" | publisher=www.astonvillaplayerdatabase.com | accessdate=11 December 2014}}</ref> He made his debut for Derby on 19 August 1934 in a 2\u20130 away defeat to [[Leicester City F.C.|Leicester City]].<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.11v11.com/matches/leicester-city-v-derby-county-19-april-1934-67274/ | title=Leicester City v Derby County 19 April 1934 | publisher=www.11v11.com | accessdate=11 December 2014}}</ref> Blore made only 15 appearances before moving to West Ham in 1935. Known as \"Vic\" by [[West Ham United F.C. supporters|West Ham fans]], he was signed by manager, [[Charlie Paynter]]. His debut came on 31 August 1935 in a 4\u20133 away defeat to [[Norwich City F.C.|Norwich City]].<ref name=whustats/> 'Keeper [[Herman Conway]] arrived later that season making Blore second-choice and with the arrival of [[Arthur Weare|Jack Weare]] from [[Wolverhampton Wanderers F.C.|Wolverhampton Wanderers]] he became third choice 'keeper. In 1936, Crystal Palace offered him regular first team football. He played for Palace until October 1938, when he signed for [[Exeter City F.C.|Exeter City]].<ref>{{cite web | url=http://theyflysohigh.co.uk/charlie-paynter/4545965284 | title=Charlie Paynter | publisher=Theyflysohigh | accessdate=11 December 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.holmesdale.net/page.php?id=319&yearfrom=1938 | title=Transfers - 1938/39 | publisher=www.holmsdate.net | accessdate=11 December 2014}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Blore, Vincent}}\n[[Category:1907 births]]\n[[Category:1997 deaths]]\n[[Category:English footballers]]\n[[Category:West Ham United F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Aston Villa F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Derby County F.C. players]]\n[[Category:English Football League players]]\n[[Category:Crystal Palace F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Exeter City F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Association football goalkeepers]]\n[[Category:Date of death unknown]]\n[[Category:Place of death unknown]]\n[[Category:Burton Town F.C. players]]\n[[Category:People from Uttoxeter]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2015}}\n{{Use British English|date=May 2015}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = Vincent Blore\n| image               = \n| fullname            = \n| height              =  \n| birth_date          = {{Birth date |1907|2|25|df=y}}\n| birth_place         = [[Uttoxeter]], England\n| death_date          = 1997\n| position            = [[Goalkeeper (association football)|Goalkeeper]]\n| years1              =\n| clubs1              = Uttoxeter Amateurs\n| years2              = {{0|000}}?\u20131932\n| clubs2              = [[Burton Town F.C.|Burton Town]]\n| years3              = 1932\u20131933\n| clubs3              = [[Aston Villa F.C.|Aston Villa]]\n| caps3               = 0\n| goals3              = 0\n| years4              = 1933\u201335\n| clubs4              = [[Derby County F.C.|Derby County]]\n| caps4               = 15\n| goals4              = 0\n| years5              = 1935\u201336\n| clubs5              = [[West Ham United F.C.|West Ham United]]\n| caps5               = 9\n| goals5              = 0\n| years6              = 1936\u201338\n| clubs6              = [[Crystal Palace F.C.|Crystal Palace]]\n| caps6               = 33\n| goals6              = 0\n| years7              = 1938\u2013{{0|000}}?\n| clubs7              = [[Exeter City F.C.|Exeter City]]\n| caps7               = \n| goals7              =\n\n}}\n'''Vincent P. Blore''' (25 February 1907 \u2013 1997)<ref name=\"whustats\">{{cite web | url=http://www.westhamstats.info/westham.php?west=2&ham=62&united=Vincent_Blore| title=Welcome to the Wonderful World of West Ham United Statistics&nbsp;\u2014 Vincent Blore | publisher=www.westhamstats.info | accessdate=11 December 2014}}</ref> also known as '''Vince Blore''' was an English [[association football|footballer]] who played as a [[goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for Uttoxeter Amateurs, [[Burton Town F.C.|Burton Town]], [[Aston Villa F.C.|Aston Villa]], [[Derby County F.C.|Derby County]], [[West Ham United F.C.|West Ham United]], [[Crystal Palace F.C.|Crystal Palace]] and [[Exeter City F.C.|Exeter City]].\n\n==Footballing career==\nBlore played for Uttoxeter Amateurs, [[Burton Town F.C.|Burton Town]] and Aston Villa before moving to Derby County in August 1933.<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.astonvillaplayerdatabase.com/134.html | title=Blore, Vincent P. \"Vic\" | publisher=www.astonvillaplayerdatabase.com | accessdate=11 December 2014}}</ref> He made his debut for Derby on 19 August 1934 in a 2-0 away defeat to [[Leicester City F.C.|Leicester City]].<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.11v11.com/matches/leicester-city-v-derby-county-19-april-1934-67274/ | title=Leicester City v Derby County 19 April 1934 | publisher=www.11v11.com | accessdate=11 December 2014}}</ref> Blore made only 15 appearances before moving to West Ham in 1935. Known as \"Vic\" by [[West Ham United F.C. supporters|West Ham fans]], he was signed by manager, [[Charlie Paynter]]. His debut came on 31 August 1935 in a 4-3 away defeat to [[Norwich City F.C.|Norwich City]].<ref name=whustats/> 'Keeper [[Herman Conway]] arrived later that season making Blore second-choice and with the arrival of [[Arthur Weare|Jack Weare]] from [[Wolverhampton Wanderers F.C.|Wolverhampton Wanderers]] he became third choice 'keeper. In 1936, Crystal Palace offered him regular first team football. He played for Palace until October 1938, when he signed for [[Exeter City F.C.|Exeter City]].<ref>{{cite web | url=http://theyflysohigh.co.uk/charlie-paynter/4545965284 | title=Charlie Paynter | publisher=Theyflysohigh | accessdate=11 December 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.holmesdale.net/page.php?id=319&yearfrom=1938 | title=Transfers - 1938/39 | publisher=www.holmsdate.net | accessdate=11 December 2014}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Blore, Vincent}}\n[[Category:1907 births]]\n[[Category:1997 deaths]]\n[[Category:English footballers]]\n[[Category:West Ham United F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Aston Villa F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Derby County F.C. players]]\n[[Category:English Football League players]]\n[[Category:Crystal Palace F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Exeter City F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Association football goalkeepers]]\n[[Category:Date of death unknown]]\n[[Category:Place of death unknown]]\n[[Category:Burton Town F.C. players]]\n[[Category:People from Uttoxeter]]\n", "name_user": "GiantSnowman", "label": "safe", "comment": "clean up,typo(s) fixed: 2-0 \u2192 2\u20130 (2)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vincent_Blore"}
